<div id="anp_a" class="d-panel p" style="display: none"><div class="notes p"><section id="historyarticle-meta1" class="history"><p>Revised 2025 Nov 12; Received 2025 Aug 29; Accepted 2025 Nov 24; Issue date 2026 Mar.</p></section></div></div>
<div id="clp_a" class="d-panel p" style="display: none">
